Package: libocmarkdown1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Markdown parsing and rendering library
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains the base markdown parsing library (libocmarkdown.so).

