Package: libollmchat1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Base library for Ollama/OpenAI API access
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains the base library for LLM API access (libollmchat.so)
 and the GTK library with chat widgets (libollmchatgtk.so).

Package: libollmchat-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libollmchat1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         libocmarkdown-dev (= ${binary:Version}),
         libocmarkdowngtk-dev (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for libollmchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains the development files for libollmchat and libollmchatgtk.

Package: ollmchat-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libocmarkdown1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Command-line tools for OLLMchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains command-line tools:
  - oc-md2html: Markdown to HTML converter
  - oc-html2md: HTML to Markdown converter

Package: ollmchat-doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Test executables and documentation for OLLMchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains test executables and documentation:
  - oc-test-cli: Command-line test executable
  - oc-test-window: GTK UI test executable
  - oc-markdown-test: Markdown parser test executable
